Package org.mapfish.print.processor.jasper

The package for processors depending on jasper and for creating jasper reports.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TableColumnConverter<R>
    Resolves a string to an image.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataSourceProcessor
    A processor that will run several other processors on a Iterable value and output a datasource object for consumption by a jasper report or sub-report.
    DataSourceProcessor.Input
    Contains the datasource input.
    DataSourceProcessor.Output
    Contains the datasource output.
    HttpImageResolver
    Interprets the text as an image URL.
    JasperReportBuilder
    A processor that actually compiles a jasper report.
    JasperReportBuilder.Input
    The input parameter object for JasperReportBuilder.
    LegendProcessor
    Create a legend.
    LegendProcessor.Input
    The Input Parameter object for LegendProcessor.
    LegendProcessor.Output
    The Output object of the legend processor method.
    MapSubReport
    Creates a Jasper report for a map, which is supposed to be embedded into an another report as sub-report.
    TableDataSource
    Processor that has data for a table in a jasper report.
    TableListProcessor
    Processor for creating a table.
    TableListProcessor.Input
    Input of processor.
    TableListProcessor.Output
    Output of processor.
    TableProcessor
    A processor for generating a table.
    TableProcessor.Input
    Input object for execute.
    TableProcessor.Output
    The Output of the processor.
